Description :
The "My Juke Box v1.0", application was developed for an assignment for “Programming for Computing” at Sheffield Hallam University.
The application shows the use of the following components, ListBoxes, TextBox and Timer. In addition, it introduces secondary Windows and covers Scope e.g., Local and Global variables.
The application was created by Student Zain Islam
